00:30:56.960 happens is there's massive engagement
00:30:59.600 because it felt current. It's
00:31:00.960 unexpected. It's relevant. And the
00:31:03.279 principle that I've seen and how it
00:31:04.960 applies to long sales cycles is
00:31:08.159 relevance plus speed typically equals
00:31:10.960 more attention, right? And so what makes
00:31:13.840 it work is it's the timeliness, it's the
00:31:16.320 relevance, and it's the speed. So many
00:31:20.799 brands oftent time will miss this window
00:31:25.200 because trends don't stay trends very
